WEBVTT

00:00:58.958 --> 00:01:01.268
"Yes, you've almost got it,"

00:01:01.292 --> 00:01:03.976
and closing slowly

00:01:04.000 --> 00:01:07.958
was -- well, it didn't really
need much translation.

00:01:09.125 --> 00:01:12.059
It turns out that Alice had taught me

00:01:12.083 --> 00:01:13.792
that everyone has a story.

00:01:14.917 --> 00:01:17.976
Everyone has a story.

00:01:18.000 --> 00:01:19.792
The challenge for the listener

00:01:20.458 --> 00:01:23.309
is how to invite it into being,

00:01:23.333 --> 00:01:25.083
and how to really hear it.

00:01:27.250 --> 00:01:30.101
